{"tid":279553,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇Izombie","createTime":"2017-06-11T11:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T05:30:21.000Z","uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"653719138af40389ed17c9120502686bdd28546b","tid":279553,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/niusnews-imgs/301294_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fniusnews-imgs%2F301294_1.jpg&h=1e806738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事敘述麗芙&middot;摩爾是一位美麗、守本份的醫學院女學生，直到某夜她參加了一個船上派對而意外地變成了殭屍。變成殭屍的她必須食用大腦來維持自己的人性，所以麗芙改行擔任驗屍官；但她只能嚐到辣味的存在，也因此使她變得愛吃辣，且還得到了能夠讀取被食用的大腦中的記憶和死者的習慣與性格。麗芙決定運用此能力來幫助他人，並協助她的上司拉維與克萊夫警探一同破解多件神祕謀殺案。<br />\n<br />\n而家播緊第3季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭兩季可以係Netflix睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a55c95e944e34882f1d21064b0230142b1704bc","tid":279553,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登冇人睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140f88c1e77870c4b99b375e85ee82172ba8f9e5","tid":279553,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"睇過下第一季"},{"pid":"154e6d0883a6deb807cfff16f5155507048e3c70","tid":279553,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過下第一季</blockquote><br />\n做咩唔追落去"},{"pid":"efe58387d70946dea5a67a593f74cc3d64d54eb1","tid":279553,"uid":11836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}